  "title": "MANAGEMENT EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p>•\tHandle hosting duties including guest reception, reservations flow, table management, and guest engagement</p><p>•\tMaintain strong floor presence to ensure smooth service flow and high service standards</p><p>•\tOversee guest experience throughout the dining and bar journey</p><p>•\tHandle and execute events including setup coordination, guest flow management, service supervision, and event wrap-up</p><p>•\tManage guest feedback professionally and resolve service-related matters promptly</p><p>•\tEnsure compliance with grooming standards, service procedures.<br /></p><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><p>•\tMinimum 2 years of experience in hospitality, F&B service, hosting, or supervisory roles</p><p>•\tStrong hosting presence with excellent guest interaction skills</p><p>•\tComfortable handling high-volume service and events</p><p>•\tWell-groomed, professional, and service-oriented</p><p>•\tAble to work flexible shifts including weekends and public holidays</p><p>•\tCalm under pressure and confident in guest-facing situations</p><p>•\tStrong sense of responsibility and accountability</p>",
